newsitem.title: USA: Nebraska fed cattle market inactive, no sales-USDA.
newsitem.headline: Nebraska fed cattle market inactive, no sales-USDA.

text.p: Steers and heifers were not tested on a dressed basis delivered (paid on hot carcass weights), USDA said.
Dressed Basis Steers - No confirmed sales.
Dressed Basis Heifers - No confirmed sales.
Slaughter steers and heifers were not tested. Demand and seller interest very light.
Weekly movement 83,700, including 16,800 previously contracted or formula cattle.
Slaughter Heifers - No confirmed sales. Sales confirmed - None For the week - None.
